{"tid":178276,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"余香凝做骨妹冧粉絲","createTime":"2017-03-29T12:14:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T21:56:50.000Z","uid":17646,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"979801138d2e0316112ee11fc861d85015590b60","tid":178276,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:14:07.000Z","msg":"今集東網節目《區區有女神》找來上位新演員余香凝（Jennifer）做主角，年僅23歲的她憑住1米73的高挑身材由模界殺入影壇，繼澳門國際影展上獲新演員獎後，又獲提名今屆香港電影金像獎「最佳新演員」，前途無限。<br />\n<br />\n今次Jennifer先帶大家到西灣河的香港電影資料館，分享她如何在此地「偷師」學演戲，她除了鍾意做演員，原來亦鍾意唱歌兼彈結他。人靚聲甜這個女神Package認真不得了！學彈結他一年多的Jennifer膽粗粗表示想挑戰街頭獻唱，務求引來途人主動點唱，才為之成功。她到公園練歌熱身壯膽時，雖偶有蝦碌情況，例如忘記歌詞或彈錯音，但無礙她於人來人往的西灣河港鐵站自彈自唱的決心。<br />\n<br />\n清唱《熱情的沙漠》<br />\n<br />\nJennifer落力獻唱期間獲多位途人賞識，其中以《這個殺手不太冷》中Leo造型現身的男街坊明顯被她電到暈陀陀，竟搞笑點唱分手歌《分手總要在雨天》送畀女友，唔怕被扭耳仔，事後更與Jennifer握手及自拍。同場「怕醜妹妹」被歌聲吸引而向Jennifer點唱情歌《紅豆》，還拍下其表演。Jennifer其後主動走上街頭，為候車的大媽獻聲。豈料對方要求她唱經典歌《熱情的沙漠》，她聞言為對方大聲清唱，獲狂讚歌喉滿分之餘，還冧爆被問：「卡拉OK有冇你啲歌呀？」Jennifer順勢呼籲大媽支持其電影，又「骨妹」上身即場為對方按摩痠痛的膊頭，引得大媽立即除下外套享受，畫面搞笑！唱到肚餓的Jennifer到太安樓掃街醫肚，還即興踩入手抓餅店學整餅，並分別為「學生妹」及「眼鏡男」親手整餅，獲餅店老闆盛讚表現。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170329/photo/bkn-20170329190048437-0329_00862_001_02b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170329%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170329190048437-0329_00862_001_02b.jpg&h=fbb427cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170329/photo/bkn-20170329190048437-0329_00862_001_03b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170329%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170329190048437-0329_00862_001_03b.jpg&h=eccf338c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170329/photo/bkn-20170329190048437-0329_00862_001_04b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170329%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170329190048437-0329_00862_001_04b.jpg&h=88ae5e45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170329/bkn-20170329190048437-0329_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170329%2Fbkn-20170329190048437-0329_00862_001.html&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIFKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=3b328cc2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170329/bkn-20170329190048437-0329_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4dea9b2eacd38ad0fb274bdc502ed0538e520f0b","tid":178276,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d3a0e72d8ef518ee496c5f2a418056b7c6e32d","tid":178276,"uid":16336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T15:14:01.000Z","msg":"咁既人都有打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e35747461abadec093e923784e4f0158957525","tid":178276,"uid":76488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T15:14:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f0d94ccb7eea80cbf47018c2323020d9cf17f8e","tid":178276,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:30:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁既人都有打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打你老母"},{"pid":"80d4e0e456d4f9633862b6a3d584b40bd4359971","tid":178276,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:39:19.000Z","msg":"賣點在哪？"},{"pid":"38dbf922f7e257c1fd8f45ae435e861802a197a5","tid":178276,"uid